{{Top|canon=GPS}}
A '''global positioning system''' or '''GPS''' was a method to calculate a position on a planetary surface. Such systems were in use during the time of the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]] and into the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]].

In [[20 BBY/Legends|20 BBY]], [[Korkie Kryze/Legends|Korkie Kryze]] and his friends rescued [[Satine Kryze/Legends|Satine Kryze]] in a speeder that had a built-in GPS.

